================================================================================

This Rust implementation is a complete rewrite of the original Python codebase.
The following components were reimplemented in Rust based on the original design:

- phone_agent/agent.py -> src/agent/phone_agent.rs
- phone_agent/actions/handler.py -> src/actions/handler.rs
- phone_agent/adb/*.py -> src/adb/*.rs
- phone_agent/config/*.py -> src/config/*.rs
- phone_agent/model/client.py -> src/model/client.rs

All code in this repository is licensed under the Apache License 2.0.
